summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of Phinney Avenue, from North Fiftieth Street to North Sixty-fifth Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, in accordance with Resolution No. 529 of the City Council of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Payment by Bonds," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
